question: According to JLL India Report Which city Ranks 7th in Most Expensive Office Locations List?
explanation: Delhi emerged as one of the most expensive premium office locations in the world. Ranked 7th in the list, rent of Delhi's premium office location is higher than San Francisco and Dubai, according to the latest report by JLL India, a real estate services firm. Mumbai is at 16th position in the list. The top spot is again taken by Hong Kong and there is the huge margin between the rent rates between Hong Kong and London (West), which is second in the list. New York, Beijing, Tokyo are on the third, fourth and fifth position respectively.
